==German==

===Etymology===
A combination of the surname of its inventor Adolphe Sax (1814-1894) + an O to make the word pronounceable + the German affix "fon", from Greek φωνή, "voice"

===Noun===
'''Saxofon''', ''n'' ([[Saxofone]])
# [[saxophone]]

====Synonyms====
* [[Saxophon]]
